caption.p: Number of Culex pipiens pipiens and Culex restuans mosquitoes collected by BGS traps in Mercer and Monmouth Counties during 2008–2011. Some specimens were not morphologically identified to species and were enumerated as Culex spp. U = unengorged, BF = blood fed, BB = black blooded, G = gravid.
